dc_title_s: Mayor's Committee on City Planning. The city of New York: Predominant use
dc_description_s: Emergency Relief Bureau. City of New York. Works Division Project. Mayor's Committee on City Planning. Shows vacant, residential, and non-residential land in New York City.
